  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2><br>\"Ladies' School Prince\" is a live interactive visual work. You will become the \"sole male student in a women's university\" and embark on a sweet and laughter-filled campus love journey from a first-person perspective! <br><br>Mysterious girl,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/af011ca62589833b0d3279b63472a25d.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/af011ca62589833b0d3279b63472a25d.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/af011ca62589833b0d3279b63472a25d.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>gentle sweetheart, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/34bd251af99a388bf0469f57d3b92586.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/34bd251af99a388bf0469f57d3b92586.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/34bd251af99a388bf0469f57d3b92586.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>cool motorcycle girl, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/4d7e76153f1d7b76728dd248cbc7f724.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/4d7e76153f1d7b76728dd248cbc7f724.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/4d7e76153f1d7b76728dd248cbc7f724.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>mature school doctor, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/a38053c28ddf1e209fc003aeb32172e5.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/a38053c28ddf1e209fc003aeb32172e5.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/a38053c28ddf1e209fc003aeb32172e5.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>playful international student,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/67c53af989bf8b92b8ca3cdc20037e9b.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/67c53af989bf8b92b8ca3cdc20037e9b.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/67c53af989bf8b92b8ca3cdc20037e9b.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>proud senior sister, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/3bf6f0e0b186739a957add6d6a2ed43d.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/3bf6f0e0b186739a957add6d6a2ed43d.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/3bf6f0e0b186739a957add6d6a2ed43d.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Amidst the temptations of various beauties, will you stay faithful or be a heartbreaker? Alternatively, will you resist the allure, focus on your studies, and create your own campus legend?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br>First-person Perspective:<br>Filmed using a first-person perspective, providing you with an immersive experience of love.<br><br>Diverse Endings:<br>Multiple game endings, including single heroine endings, dual heroine endings, multiplayer endings, and the challenging \"human limit\" ending for the lone wolf in the girls' school, await your exploration!<br><br>Innovative Gameplay:<br>Your choices directly influence the storyline development. During the exploration of the game, you can collect various in-game items and use them to unlock hidden plotlines.<br><br>Superb Visuals:<br>In the campus life, six main heroines with different personalities will bring you unique romantic experiences!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team Introduction</h2>From Production Team:<br><br>While we hope to receive appreciation and encouragement from players, we also firmly embrace their criticism. In the end, let's borrow a quote from \"Ready Player One\": \"Thank you for playing my game, thank you for coming to my world, thank you for filling the voids of my past regrets.”",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2><br>\"Ladies' School Prince\" is a live interactive visual work. You will become the \"sole male student in a women's university\" and embark on a sweet and laughter-filled campus love journey from a first-person perspective! <br><br>Mysterious girl,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/af011ca62589833b0d3279b63472a25d.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/af011ca62589833b0d3279b63472a25d.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/af011ca62589833b0d3279b63472a25d.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>gentle sweetheart, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/34bd251af99a388bf0469f57d3b92586.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/34bd251af99a388bf0469f57d3b92586.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/34bd251af99a388bf0469f57d3b92586.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>cool motorcycle girl, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/4d7e76153f1d7b76728dd248cbc7f724.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/4d7e76153f1d7b76728dd248cbc7f724.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/4d7e76153f1d7b76728dd248cbc7f724.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>mature school doctor, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/a38053c28ddf1e209fc003aeb32172e5.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/a38053c28ddf1e209fc003aeb32172e5.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/a38053c28ddf1e209fc003aeb32172e5.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>playful international student,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/67c53af989bf8b92b8ca3cdc20037e9b.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/67c53af989bf8b92b8ca3cdc20037e9b.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/67c53af989bf8b92b8ca3cdc20037e9b.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>proud senior sister, <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/3bf6f0e0b186739a957add6d6a2ed43d.poster.avif?t=1757668350\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/3bf6f0e0b186739a957add6d6a2ed43d.webm?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786680/extras/3bf6f0e0b186739a957add6d6a2ed43d.mp4?t=1757668350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Amidst the temptations of various beauties, will you stay faithful or be a heartbreaker? Alternatively, will you resist the allure, focus on your studies, and create your own campus legend?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br>First-person Perspective:<br>Filmed using a first-person perspective, providing you with an immersive experience of love.<br><br>Diverse Endings:<br>Multiple game endings, including single heroine endings, dual heroine endings, multiplayer endings, and the challenging \"human limit\" ending for the lone wolf in the girls' school, await your exploration!<br><br>Innovative Gameplay:<br>Your choices directly influence the storyline development. During the exploration of the game, you can collect various in-game items and use them to unlock hidden plotlines.<br><br>Superb Visuals:<br>In the campus life, six main heroines with different personalities will bring you unique romantic experiences!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team Introduction</h2>From Production Team:<br><br>While we hope to receive appreciation and encouragement from players, we also firmly embrace their criticism. In the end, let's borrow a quote from \"Ready Player One\": \"Thank you for playing my game, thank you for coming to my world, thank you for filling the voids of my past regrets.”",
